Measles in Central California: KFSN investigates vaccine rates in 6 California counties.
https://abc30.com/health/return-of-measles-in-central-california/5556390/

Measles in San Francisco: KGO investigates vaccination rates in 9 Bay Area counties.
https://abc7news.com/health/sonoma-county-schools-one-of-least-immunized-from-measles-/5555828/

Measles in Houston: KTRK investigates vaccine rates in Texas. https://abc13.com/5556274/

