Monroe County leaders said a person with measles recently traveled through the county. County Executive Cheryl Dinolfo said the person was in the county for new employee orientation at CGS Fabrications in Webster.

[See source URL for locations of possible exposure.]

"We know based on the information provided that this individual on [21 Sep 2019] developed a rash," Dinolfo said.

